This will enable the selection of which bank account should be printed on the document. This is enabled by default. 

The bank account to be printed is determined by the field `Print Bank Account` on the payment method used on the document. The following values are currently available:
- **Our Bank Account** (default): Print the bank account specified on the `EOS Our Bank Account` field.
- **Cust./.Vend Bank Account**: Print the first bank account of the `Bill-To Customer` / `Pay-To Vendor`, if there is one.
- **Document Bank Account** (only available with Advanced Document Report for Italy): Prints the customer/vendor bank account that was specified using the field `Bank Account` on the document.

This behaviour can be customized using the `OnBeforeGetBankAccount` event on codeunit ` 18122055 EOS009 LE Bank Account`.